Program: Discovery
Title: Polio vaccine
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwfk
Last Broadcast Date: 25 April 1995
How a polio vaccine with an unlimited shelf life could help eradicate the disease for good. A sugar-based vaccine which doesn't need refrigeration is being developed by a Cambridge-based company in the UK. Also in the programme, how bananas could help protect against Hepatitis B and how are ear can tune into to different sounds. Show less